cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with statistical machine translation for dialectal Arabic. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the study involves data selection strategies. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as machine learning techniques are used to develop the data selection strategies and improve the machine translation system. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SD (Sound) as the study involves the transcription and translation of spoken language.
